= Action name = PCK.AUTOMIC_TENABLE_IO.PUB.ACTION.UPDATE_SCAN
= General Description = This action updates a scan in Tenable.io.
= Inputs = - Scan ID* : Provide ID or UUID of a Scan to be updated. - Name : Provide a name to the scan. - Description : Provide a short description for the scan to be created. - Folder ID : Provide unique ID of the destination folder for the scan. E.g. 52 - Scanner ID : Provide the unique ID of the scanner to use. E.g. 110973 - Enabled* : Specify whether the schedule for the scan is enabled or not. - Launch : Specify when to launch the scan. (i.e. DAILY, WEEKLY, MONTHLY, YEARLY) - Start Time : Specify the starting time and date for the scan (i.e. YYYYMMDDTHHMMSS). - Rules : Expects a semi-colon delimited string comprised of three values. The frequency (FREQ=ONETIME or DAILY or WEEKLY or MONTHLY or YEARLY), the interval (INTERVAL=1 or 2 or 3 ... x), and the days of the week (BYDAY=SU,MO,TU,WE,TH,FR,SA). To create a scan that runs every three weeks on Monday Wednesday and Friday the string would be 'FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=3;BYDAY=MO,WE,FR' - Time Zone : Specify the timezone for the scan schedule. - Target Groups : Provide list of Target Groups separated by comma to scan. E.g. "143","145" - Agent Groups : Provide list of Agent Groups separated by comma to scan. E.g. "e610d266-1d58-4a99-b859-0d67b9423079","e610d266-1d58-4a99-b859-0d67b9423079" - Targets : Provide list of Targets separated by comma to scan. E.g. 10.243.12.23(for basic network scan) - File Targets : The name of a file containing the list of targets to scan. This file must be uploaded at tenable.io. E.g. uploadedTargets.txt - Emails : Provide comma-separated list of accounts that receive the email summary report. - ACLs : Provide a list of json of permissions to apply to the scan. E.g. {"permissions": 128, "type": "default"}, {"permissions": 64, "type": "user"}
= Behaviour = - If Scan is a non agent type than Targets is a mandatory field if Target Groups is not provided. Else Target Groups is mandatory for other scan types.
= Example = - Scan ID* : 53 - Name : Updated Scan - Description : We are Updating this scan - Folder ID : 52 - Scanner ID : 110973 - Enabled* : true - Launch : DAILY - Start Time : 2019071010:30:35 - Rules : FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=3;BYDAY=MO,WE,FR - Time Zone : Africa/Accra - Target Groups : "143","145" - Agent Groups : "e610d266-1d58-4a99-b859-0d67b9423079" - Targets : 10.243.12.23 - File Targets : uploadedTargets.txt - Emails : ABC@broadcom.com - ACLs : {"permissions": 128, "type": "default"}, {"permissions": 64, "type": "user"}
